genresAdvancedInfo.name: swiss worship
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A genre of Christian music that has gained popularity in Switzerland, Swiss Worship features uplifting lyrics, soaring melodies, and a focus on praising God. Many Swiss Worship songs are performed in both German and French, reflecting the country's linguistic diversity. Artists like ICF Worship and Worship Central Switzerland are popular in the genre.
